snippet.title: Catlandia Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
Catlandia is a 2D RPG — with cats!

Fight vicious dogs. Befriend cats. Embark upon useful quests. Customize and dress up your cat!

Available on PC/Mac on Steam, plus Android and iOS!
